snippet.title: RESOGUN Defenders Expansion PS4 | Exclusive to PlayStation
snippet.description: Blast your way into a blistering battle of survival and pitch a desperate last stand. Unleash a diverse array of devastating weapons including lasers, missiles and nova-bombs against a vicious alien army.
